    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_jc.00475_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="center">Home</name>
                    <date when="1877-01-31"><choice><sic>Wednsday</sic><corr>Wednesday</corr></choice> Evening</date>
                    <date when="1877-01-31" rend="right">Jan 31/77</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear friend</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>we <choice><sic>recieved</sic><corr>received</corr></choice> your <choice><sic>wellcome</sic><corr>welcome</corr></choice> Letter last <choice><sic>evenigng</sic><corr>evening</corr></choice> &amp; was glad to hear from you &amp; to know that you are well <unclear reason="damage" cert="medium" resp="#vm">&amp;</unclear> happy with your friends in the <unclear reason="damage" cert="medium" resp="#vm">City</unclear>.<ptr target="n0817"/> we are all well as usual I have just <unclear reason="damage" cert="high" resp="#vm">returned</unclear> home from Red Bank where I w<gap reason="damage" extent="two partial words" quantity="4" unit="chars"/><unclear reason="damage" cert="medium" resp="#km">illed to</unclear> <choice><sic>se</sic><corr>see</corr></choice> of my Dear Mother who is at this time to all <choice><sic>appearences</sic><corr>appearances</corr></choice> near Death <choice><sic>to day</sic><corr>today</corr></choice> when I left her I felt that it <unclear reason="damage" cert="high" resp="#vm">would</unclear> be the last time that I should <choice><sic>se</sic><corr>see</corr></choice> her alive. Dear <choice><sic>frend</sic><corr>friend</corr></choice> you can judge of my feelings better than I <choice><abbr>cn</abbr><expan>can</expan></choice> <choice><sic>discribe</sic><corr>describe</corr></choice> them. we shall look <choice><sic>fore</sic><corr>for</corr></choice> you down with us <choice><sic>Teusday</sic><corr>Tuesday</corr></choice> but please do not think of
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_jc.00476_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc_jc.00477_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            
            going back in one day I <choice><sic>shoul</sic><corr>should</corr></choice> not get <del>go</del> to <choice><sic>se</sic><corr>see</corr></choice> you at all</p>
            
            <p>surely you can give us more Than one day from your friends I know they can make you more <choice><sic>comefortable</sic><corr>comfortable</corr></choice> than we can but they do not care <choice><sic>fore</sic><corr>for</corr></choice> you more than we <gap reason="damage" extent="several words" quantity="18" unit="chars"/>tions</p>
            
            <closer>
                <salute>ever your friend</salute>
                <signed>S M. Stafford</signed>
            </closer>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc_jc.00478_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            
        </body>
